      "rationale": "Validation performed on production-intent 7.5 mm non-cannulated screw geometry under ASTM F1717 loading, which directly represents the COU. Two independent laboratories (FDA CDRH and DePuy Synthes) conducted testing, providing cross-laboratory reproducibility confirmation. COU boundary conditions are fully represented by the validation scenario. Gradation 3 achieved."
